 - HltCommon/HltAlgorithm.h : the base class for HLT algorithm
     - deals with input/output tracks and vertices
     - deals with the summary
     - deals with input/output histograms and upgrading them
     - deals with the conditions
 - HltCommon/HltContainers.h : containers used in HLT (normal std::vector)
 - HltCommon/IHltDataStore.h : interface to a storege tools
     - that holds the collections of tracks and vertex (logical) containers
     - and the summary
 - HltCommon/HltUtils.h: common c-functions used in HLT
 - HltCommon/HltFunctions.h : common functions used in HLT
 - HltCommon/HltSequences.h : common loop in containers in HLT
 - HltCommon/EFunctions.h: template funtions (a la LoKi)	
 - HltCommon/ESequences.h: template loops in containers (a la LoKi)
 - HltCommon/ParserDescriptor.h : helper class to parser a string option

 - src/HltAlgorithm.cpp : code of the base class
 - src/HltDataStore.h   : implementation of the hlt data store 
 - src/HltDataInit.h    : deals with the initialization of the Hlt
 - src/HltDataEnd.h     : deals with the end, locate objects in TES
 - src/HltMonitor.h     : simple implementation of the monitoring
 - src/HltSequencer.h   : sequencer with extra functionality for HLT
 - src/HltTrackIPSelection.h : alg to select tracks in a given IP window
 - src/HltUtils.cpp     : code of the c-functions of the HLT
 - src/L0Entry.h        : algo to enter in a ally
 - src/ParseDescriptor.cpp : helper code to parse a strip option

